PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774271469
OL,3,CWordsworth Grasmere launches daffodil
OL,4,Ctrail to celebrate famous poem
OL,6,FFrom the historic interiors of Dove
OL,7,FCottage, visitors are directed through
OL,8,Fthe Garden-Orchard and Woodland Walk,
OL,9,Fwhere a ceramic daffodil instillation
OL,10,Fis situated.
OL,12,FThe display was created by Helen
OL,13,FRatcliffe, a potter based in the Lake
OL,14,FDistrict, alongside Penrith charity
OL,15,F'Another Way'.
OL,17,FThe daffodils have been arranged to
OL,18,Fevoke Dorothy Wordsworth's description
OL,19,Fof the flowers "dancing" beside
OL,20,FUllswater.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
