PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774271469
OL,3,CWordsworth Grasmere launches daffodil
OL,4,Ctrail to celebrate famous poem
OL,6,FThe trail ends in the Wordsworth
OL,7,FMuseum, where early print editions of
OL,8,F'I wandered lonely as a Cloud' are on
OL,9,Fdisplay alongside original journal
OL,10,Fmanuscripts from Dorothy Wordsworth.
OL,12,FMelissa Mitchell, Curator for
OL,13,FWordsworth Grasmere said: "Our new
OL,14,Ftrail invites you to explore one of
OL,15,FWordsworth's most popular and
OL,16,Frecognisable poems in the very place
OL,17,Fit was written: Dove Cottage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
